---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Disclaimer · Pro Se Fair Play Mediation"
  description="Legal disclaimer for Pro Se Fair Play Mediation & Document Preparation Services, LLC."
>
  <!-- ========================== HEADER ========================== -->
  <header class="legal-header">
    <div class="container legal-header-inner">
      <p class="kicker reveal reveal-d1">
        <a href="/" class="back-link">
          <span class="arrow-left" aria-hidden="true">←</span>
          Home
        </a>
        <span class="kicker-sep" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
        Legal
      </p>
      <h1 class="display legal-title reveal reveal-d2">Disclaimer</h1>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- ========================== BODY ========================== -->
  <section class="legal-body">
    <div class="container-narrow legal-prose">
      <p>
        Pro Se Fair Play Mediation LLC is not a law firm, and I am not
        acting as your attorney or legal representative. I do not provide
        legal advice, legal strategy, tax advice, financial advice, or
        representation in court. All mediation and document preparation
        services are provided for self-represented individuals seeking
        assistance with organizing and preparing family law documents and
        facilitating structured discussions between parties.
      </p>

      <p>
        Clients are strongly encouraged to consult with an independent
        attorney, financial advisor, accountant, or other qualified
        professional prior to signing, filing, or relying upon any
        agreement or court document to ensure they fully understand their
        legal rights, obligations, and the potential legal and financial
        consequences of their decisions.
      </p>

      <p>
        All documents are prepared based solely upon the information,
        representations, and documentation provided by the parties.
        Clients are solely responsible for reviewing all documents for
        accuracy and completeness prior to filing with the court. Pro Se
        Fair Play Mediation LLC does not guarantee any legal outcome,
        court approval, or specific result in any matter and shall not be
        held responsible for decisions made by the parties, court rulings,
        filing errors, rejected filings, or the legal consequences arising
        from the use of any prepared documents.
      </p>

      <p>
        Clients are responsible for filing their own documents with the
        appropriate court. I do not file documents on behalf of clients,
        appear in court, represent parties in legal proceedings,
        communicate with judges on behalf of clients, or act as legal
        counsel in any capacity.
      </p>

      <p>
        My role is to provide a professional, organized, and neutral
        process designed to help clients feel more informed, prepared, and
        supported while navigating family law matters independently.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-header {
    position: relative;
    padding-block: clamp(4rem, 6vw + 1rem, 6rem) clamp(2rem, 3vw, 3rem);
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, rgba(196, 154, 75, 0.08), transparent 55%),
      var(--color-cream);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-divider);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .legal-header-inner { position: relative; max-width: 64rem; }
  .back-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-gold-deep);
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .back-link:hover { color: var(--color-navy); }
  .arrow-left { transition: transform 0.3s var(--ease-out); }
  .back-link:hover .arrow-left { transform: translateX(-3px); }
  .kicker-sep { color: var(--color-divider); margin-inline: 0.4rem; }
  .legal-title {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: var(--step-5);
    line-height: 1.02;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .legal-body {
    padding-block: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-3xl);
    background: var(--color-cream);
  }
  .legal-prose {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--step-1);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
  }
  .legal-prose p + p { margin-top: 1.25rem; }
  .legal-prose ul {
    margin-block: 1.25rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.45rem;
  }
  .legal-prose li {
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .legal-title { font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 1.8rem + 3vw, 3.5rem); }
  }
</style>
